{
  "stem": "6277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some smuggled in their children, a few of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were even a few--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a few women who dressed up as men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was only a few of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But most, it was working-- working people, working people, men who-- who went to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know exactly from the few who went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some of the women survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in that time, when they were taken, they took about 200 women, they took to the jail as seamstresses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came later when the action was gone and so they took them in a house-- and actually, it was two or three houses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a few hundred's left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them survived, very, very, really, very few.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the ghetto-- from the ghetto, we lived on [INAUDIBLE] Street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, again, crowded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in  a small room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have two-- two tiers, blank beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we would put one--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the other, bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were eight people in a small room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the morning, early in the morning, you were chased to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody has his-- his column here, his work-- work group, or whatever it's called.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was working in the beginning, on Smilsu iela, or [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sand ?] Street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was working as a janitor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I clean the-- the street, the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were cutting wood, heating the oven-- oven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There-- there was the central heating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we were working there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And conditions, it was hard work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would risk to get something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you had-- you-- you would meet some people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
